The empties? Don't ask me what happens to them.

1124
01:01:30,187 --> 01:01:31,554
为什么 废容器怎么样了?
Why, what happens to the empties?

1125
01:01:31,555 --> 01:01:33,255
我告诉过你不要问我!
I told you not to ask me that!

1126
01:01:33,256 --> 01:01:35,532
快走! 快离开这里 否则就太晚了!
Go! Get out, before it's too late!

1127
01:01:39,629 --> 01:01:41,631
