1157
01:03:03,079 --> 01:03:04,213
我们得离开这个镇子
We've gotta get out of town,

1158
01:03:04,214 --> 01:03:05,625
我们得在事情恶化之前离开这里
we've gotta get beyond it before it's too late.

1159
01:03:05,882 --> 01:03:07,650
