That morning gave a whole new meaning to the word "hangover".

1696
01:38:59,667 --> 01:39:03,638
我们决定散步解酒 一路走回了伦敦
We decided to walk it off, all the way back to London,

1697
01:39:04,505 --> 01:39:08,146
